description:
A dataset of glioma biopsies which were examined using hyperspectral imaging. The details of the acquisition protocol and description of the data are provided in the accompaniying paper: 
 "A transportable hyperspectral imaging setup based on fast, high-density spectral scanning for in situ quantitative biochemical mapping of fresh tissue biopsies", Luca Giannoni et. al. 
 &nbsp;

